      <title>舒尔茨称已准备好讨论德国提前大选的时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/scholz-says-ready-to-discuss-timing-of-germany-s-snap-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨表示，只要反对派议员支持他在任期结束前推动议会通过的立法，他愿意讨论提前举行选举的时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/scholz-says-ready-to-discuss-timing-of-germany-s-snap-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 14:54:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选后英国与欧盟加快防务协议谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/uk-and-eu-hasten-work-on-defense-pact-after-trump-s-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的当选引发了欧洲的担忧，即在美国对乌克兰的支持可能减少的情况下，欧盟将需要增加对乌克兰的援助，欧盟正寻求加快与英国就新的防务和安全协议进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/uk-and-eu-hasten-work-on-defense-pact-after-trump-s-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 14:29:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Burford Capital 愿意发行价值 160 亿美元的阿根廷债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/argentina-hasn-t-come-to-negotiating-table-in-16-billion-ypf-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，十多年前，投资者在阿根廷因国有化能源公司 YPF SA 而赢得 160 亿美元判决后，愿意以债券而非现金形式获得支付。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/argentina-hasn-t-come-to-negotiating-table-in-16-billion-ypf-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 14:08:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
