    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰总理呼吁举行选举并寻求解散议会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/irish-election-triggered-as-pm-requests-parliament-be-dissolved</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰总理西蒙·哈里斯于周五下午正式宣布提前举行大选，投票将于 11 月 29 日举行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/irish-election-triggered-as-pm-requests-parliament-be-dissolved</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 13:48:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>若特朗普停止援助乌克兰，欧盟将考虑增加援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/eu-is-looking-at-ramping-up-ukraine-aid-if-trump-pulls-the-plug</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟领导人正在试图确定，如果唐纳德·特朗普决定停止美国的支持，他们是否能够继续支持乌克兰的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/eu-is-looking-at-ramping-up-ukraine-aid-if-trump-pulls-the-plug</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 11:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克首都在暴力抗议后恢复平静</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/mozambique-protests-calm-returns-to-maputo-after-deadly-clashes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，警方使用致命暴力驱散了前一天席卷马普托的选举后抗议浪潮，莫桑比克首都恢复了平静。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/mozambique-protests-calm-returns-to-maputo-after-deadly-clashes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 09:00:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
